Description_lang: Initial damage from your Bear will consume Serpent Sting from up to $s1 nearby targets, dealing $s2% of its remaining damage instantly.

description_blz.en_US: Initial damage from your Bear will consume Serpent Sting from up to 8 nearby targets, dealing 100% of its remaining damage instantly.
description_blz.es_MX: El daño inicial de tu oso consume Picadura de serpiente de hasta 8 objetivos cercanos, lo que inflige un 100% del daño restante instantáneamente.
description_blz.pt_BR: O dano inicial do seu Urso consome Picada de Serpente de até 8 alvos próximos, causando 100% do dano restante instantaneamente.
description_blz.de_DE: Der Initialschaden Eures Bären verbraucht 'Schlangengift' auf bis zu 8 Zielen in der Nähe und verursacht sofort 100% des verbleibenden Schadens.
description_blz.en_GB: Initial damage from your Bear will consume Serpent Sting from up to 8 nearby targets, dealing 100% of its remaining damage instantly.
description_blz.es_ES: El daño inicial de tu oso consume Picadura de serpiente de hasta 8 objetivos cercanos, lo que inflige al instante un 100% de su daño restante.
description_blz.fr_FR: Les dégâts initiaux infligés par votre ours consomment l’effet Morsure de serpent sur un maximum de 8 cibles proches, infligeant instantanément 100 % des dégâts restants.
description_blz.it_IT: I danni iniziali inflitti dal tuo Orso consumano Morso del Serpente da massimo 8 bersagli vicini, infliggendo il 100% dei danni restanti istantaneamente.
description_blz.ru_RU: Первоначальный урон от атаки вашего медведя поглощает "Укус змеи" с 8 ближайших целей и мгновенно наносит 100% оставшегося урона.
description_blz.ko_KR: 곰이 최초 피해를 입힐 때 최대 8명의 주위 대상에게 걸린 독사 쐐기를 소모하여 즉시 남은 피해의 100%를 입힙니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 你的熊的初始傷害會消耗附近最多8個目標身上的毒蛇釘刺，立刻造成相當於其剩餘傷害100%的傷害。
description_blz.zh_CN: 你的巨熊的初始伤害会消耗最多8个附近目标身上的毒蛇钉刺，立即造成其剩余伤害的100%。
